abstract: Report by Ohio State Atty Gen Mike DeWine finds three Planned Parenthood clinics violated no laws by selling fetal tissue but disposed of fetuses improperly by giving them to disposal companies that take remains to landfills.
lead_paragraph: An investigation into whether three Planned Parenthood clinics had improperly sold fetal tissue found that they had not, but said that they disposed of aborted fetuses improperly..

headline.main: Ohio: Objection to Disposal Practices at Planned Parenthood Clinics
headline.print_headline: Ohio: New Objection Is Raised Over Planned Parenthood Clinics
